cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.SI, cs.SP. 

The paper deals with compressed sensing and sparse signal recovery, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), signal processing (cs.SP), and statistics (cs.SI). The use of reweighted $l_1$ minimization and the development of a modified iterative reweighted $l_1$ minimization algorithm also suggest a focus on optimization and algorithms, which are common in these sub-categories.
